<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ي ظ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَيْظُ)</span> حَمَارَّةُ الصَّيْفِ. وَ <span class="c2">(قَاظَ)</span> بِالْمَكَانِ وَ <span class="c2">(تَقَيَّظَ)</span> بِهِ أَقَامَ بِهِ فِي الصَّيْفِ وَالْمَوْضِعُ <span class="c2">(مَقِيظٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(قَاظَ)</span> يَوْمُنَا اشْتَدَّ حَرُّهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>